<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "This ontology models semantically the EUDAMED cataloge, including devices, manufacturers, identified risks, incidents and security corrective actions." .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> " Andoni Rodriguez Benito" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2026-04-26"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> " Andoni Rodriguez Benito" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "An ontology about the european cataloge of high risk medical devices and in vitro diagnosis devices, inside the regulatory framework MDR (EU 2017/745) and IVDR (EU 2017/746)" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "High risk medical and in-vitro diagnostics devices (MDR and IVDR compliant)" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "RC-PEC2-AndoniRodriguezBenito" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "0.0.1" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/txony/ontologies/2026/3/RC_PEC2_Andoni_Rodriguez_Benito> <https://w3id.org/widoco/vocab#introduction> "The goal of the ontology is to allow the accurate share of data among manufacturers, regulatory entities, hospitals and patients." .
